ar.com.hjg.pngj

Class PngReaderDumb

  • java.lang.Object
    • ar.com.hjg.pngj.PngReaderDumb

  • public class PngReaderDumb
extends Object
    Sample implementation of a very basic reader that only loads the empty chunks (except the IHDR). The IDAT are optional.
